high_descs: Turn left and go to the small black table.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Go to the sink on your right.
Go to the white table on your left.
Put the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed apple on the white table.

high_descs: Turn left and go back to the black table.
Pick up the apple from the left side of the table.
Take the apple and move to the right to go to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the apple.
Carry the apple and turn around to go to the white table on the right.
Place the apple on the white table, to the right of the apple already there.
anns.task_desc: Rinse an apple and place it on a table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the black table
Pick up an apple off of the table
Move right and then turn to face left to look at the sink
Drop the apple in the sink and run the faucet for a few seconds, then pick up the apple again
Turn around and then turn right to face the white table
Set the apple down on the table
anns.task_desc: Rinse an apple and set it down on the table
